text: Marija Goranović (born 22 October 1995) is a Montenegrin footballer who plays as a defender. She has been a member of the Montenegro women's national team. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Montenegrin women's footballers Category:Montenegro women's international footballers Category:ŽFK Ekonomist players
